            <div class="comment-body js-comment-edit-hide">
                
                <span class="comment-copy">For PHP &lt; 5.5 there is polyfill for <code>array_column</code> function <a href="https://github.com/ramsey/array_column" rel="nofollow noreferrer">github.com/ramsey/array_column</a>. So it's possible to use more elegant way from second code snippet on legacy versions.</span>
                
                <div class="d-inline-flex ai-center">
