    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>if you want to sort multi dimentional array </p>

<p>first array is :</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$results</span>[<span class="hljs-string">'total_quote_sales_person_wise'</span>][<span class="hljs-string">'quote_po'</span>];
</code></pre>

<p>second one is :</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$results</span>[<span class="hljs-string">'total_quote_sales_person_wise'</span>][<span class="hljs-string">'quote_count'</span>];
</code></pre>

<p>this both multidimentional array you want to sort descending order at one time then use this code :</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">array_multisort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$results</span>[<span class="hljs-string">'total_quote_sales_person_wise'</span>][<span class="hljs-string">'quote_po'</span>],SORT_DESC, <span class="hljs-variable">$results</span>[<span class="hljs-string">'total_quote_sales_person_wise'</span>][<span class="hljs-string">'quote_count'</span>],SORT_DESC);
</code></pre>
    </div>
